.Ss Module ngx_http_split_clients_module
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Ic split_clients Ar string Ar $variable Brq No ...
.Bl -tag -width Ds -compact
.It default:
.It context: Ic http
.El
.Pp
Creates a variable for A/B testing, for example:
